text: Kilchberg is a municipality of the district of Horgen in the canton of Zurich in Switzerland. ==Industry== It is home to the corporate headquarters of the confectionery Lindt & Sprüngli. ==Gallery== File:Kilchberg Juli 2011.JPG|Kilchberg File:Zürichsee - Kilchberg Lindt & Sprüngli IMG 0227.JPG|Lindt & Sprüngli ==References== ==Other websites== * Official Website * Lindt & Sprüngli Official Website * Category:Municipalities in Horgen
